lua provides CMake targets:

  find_package(unofficial-lua CONFIG REQUIRED)
  target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE unofficial::lua::lua)
  target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE unofficial::lua::lua-cpp)

  CMake can drive program execution with targets:
  unofficial::lua::lua-compiler
  unofficial::lua::lua-interpreter

  add_custom_command(..
    COMMAND $<TARGET_FILE:unofficial::lua::lua-interpreter> ..
    ...
  )
